# 🌐 Code of Conduct

As contributors and maintainers of WICCI-NAC repositories, we are committed to creating an open, respectful, and inclusive community.

## 📜 Our Pledge

We pledge to make participation in our project a harassment-free experience for everyone, regardless of:

- Gender, gender identity, and expression  
- Age, disability, ethnicity, religion, or nationality  
- Personal appearance or background  
- Political or academic affiliation

## ✅ Expected Behavior

- Be respectful, inclusive, and open to feedback.
- Use welcoming and inclusive language.
- Accept constructive criticism with grace.

## 🚫 Unacceptable Behavior

- Harassment, discrimination, or derogatory comments
- Political or personal attacks
- Publishing others' private information

## 💬 Reporting Issues

If you witness or experience any violation of this Code of Conduct, please email us at:

📧 **lynnfrederickdsouza@gmail.com**

All reports will be handled with confidentiality and care.

---

This Code of Conduct is adapted from the [Contributor Covenant](https://www.contributor-covenant.org), version 2.1.
